INSERT INTO `log` VALUES ('604', '2023-10-02 16:32:05', 'Review assignment 2659-45 deleted by chair', 'review', '{\"paperid\":\"2659\",\"reviewerid\":\"45\",\"completed\":\"T\",\"assigned\":\"2023-07-05\",\"updated\":\"2023-08-05\",\"score\":\"1\",\"recommendation\":\"1\",\"category\":\"1\",\"value\":\"5\",\"familiar\":\"High\",\"bpcandidate\":\"No\",\"length\":\"No\",\"difference\":\"4\",\"pccomments\":null,\"authorcomments\":\"0 Abstract\\r\\nObtained results are not detailed in abstract. \\r\\nUsed metholodgy is not described in the abstract.\\r\\n\\r\\n1 Introduction\\r\\nAuthor writes that propose of the article is: (1)Develop a software tool (2)with an innovative pedagogical approach (3) improve the learning process of children with emphasis on psychomotor and psychoanalytic disabilities and attention deficits.\\r\\nSo, sections along the article needs to be evidenced clearly the compliance with the propose.\\r\\nSome references are missed. \\r\\n\\r\\n2 Related Work \\r\\nSome studiess related to gamification are presented. \\r\\nAuthor needs to evidence that his proposal will be fill a gap and What is the added value compared to existing proposals.\\r\\n\\r\\n3. Methodology\\r\\nA Systematic description of Methodology is not described by the author. \\r\\nFigure 1 describes \\\"developing phases of the tool\\\", however activities of methodology design are not described either the methods that will be applied in order to achieve the proposal of the article.\\r\\nthis section needs to be rewritten\\r\\n\\r\\n4. Proposed approach\\r\\nThere is no agreement between section 4 and section 3, this is due to the lack of definition of the activities of the methodological design.\\r\\nThere is no evidence of the techniques or methods used to define the functional requirements as well as how the games that allow the objectives mentioned by the author were chosen.\\r\\n\\r\\n5. Conclusion. \\r\\nThe questionnaire is not a sufficient evidence to affirm tha the tool is h